I've toying around earlier today, a little last night with characters, seeing which one I'd like.<br>
<br>
It's acually ironic you say you need a Necro, for my Primary on Quellious was a Necro ( 53, and retired ). What sort of Necromancer are you looking for? I could go from Infernalist, to Seeker of Truth, to a seeker of balance ( Although, try and do that and worship a dark god at the same time o_0 )<br>
<br>
The Vah Shir rogue sounds intriguing. I've never tried a rogue, and I haven't played much Vah Shir.<br>
<br>
For the idea of the Vah Shir: What would your opinion of them be?<br>
<br>
Myself, I see them as a neutral, shamanitic society, who seek to better themselves, and their surrounding homeland. Since all of them are agnostic, they don't seem to have any sort of devotions of any sort to any particular god. To me, that would signify that the religion of Shar Vhal could be a Paganistic, or mabye even naturalistic.<br>
<br>
Fascinating.<br>
<br>
Maybe I'll do just that...<br>
<br>
But in the mean how, I gotta go contribute to the American economy. I'll swing by later. Thank you all again for the warm welcome!<br>
